sa:

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/tab/columns[`dba_tab_columns`] is related to `dba_tab_cols`, the difference being that `dba_tab_columns` only shows columns that are
   not generated, see → development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/tab/columns/diff-tab_cols[differences between `dba_tab_columns` and `dba_tab_cols`].

  → development/databases/Oracle/installed/data-dictionary/tab/columns[`dba_tab_columns`]

